<Link id="l01401" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1401"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   - There should never be any negative offsets here.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01402" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1402"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
